{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Spec Validation Gate",
  "description": "Validates spec structure when spec files are edited. Ensures proposal, requirements, design, and tasks follow the required format before implementation begins.",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileEdited",
    "patterns": [
      ".kiro/specs/**/*.md"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "# Spec Validation Gate\n\nWhen any file in `.kiro/specs/` is created or modified, validate the spec folder structure and content quality.\n\n## Validation Rules\n\n### 1. Folder Completeness\nCheck that the spec folder contains all required files:\n- `proposal.md` ‚Äî REQUIRED\n- `requirements.md` ‚Äî REQUIRED\n- `design.md` ‚Äî REQUIRED (can be minimal for small changes)\n- `tasks.md` ‚Äî REQUIRED\n\nIf any are missing, warn the user: \"Spec `<name>` is incomplete. Missing: <files>. Use `spec-propose` to generate the full structure.\"\n\n### 2. Proposal Validation\n`proposal.md` must contain:\n- [ ] A `## Problem Statement` section (not empty)\n- [ ] A `## Proposed Solution` section (not empty)\n- [ ] A `## Scope` section with at least one in-scope item\n\nIf missing, warn: \"proposal.md is missing required sections. A proposal needs at minimum: Problem Statement, Proposed Solution, and Scope.\"\n\n### 3. Requirements Validation\n`requirements.md` must contain:\n- [ ] At least one `### REQ-` heading\n- [ ] Each requirement has `**Acceptance Criteria:**` with at least one checkbox item `- [ ]`\n\nIf requirements lack acceptance criteria, warn: \"REQ-<N> has no acceptance criteria. Requirements must be testable ‚Äî add `- [ ] criterion` items.\"\n\n### 4. Tasks Validation\n`tasks.md` must contain:\n- [ ] At least one checkbox item (`- [ ]` or `- [x]`)\n- [ ] Tasks should be atomic (warn if any task description exceeds 200 characters)\n\n### 5. Cross-Reference Check\n- If `design.md` exists and references requirement IDs (REQ-1, REQ-2), verify those IDs exist in `requirements.md`\n- If `tasks.md` references requirement IDs, verify they exist\n\n## Severity\n\n- Missing files: **ERROR** ‚Äî block implementation\n- Missing sections in proposal: **WARNING** ‚Äî allow but flag\n- Requirements without acceptance criteria: **ERROR** ‚Äî block implementation\n- Empty tasks: **WARNING** ‚Äî allow but flag\n- Broken cross-references: **WARNING** ‚Äî flag for correction\n\n## Output\n\nSummarize validation results:\n```\nSpec Validation: <spec-name>\n‚úÖ proposal.md ‚Äî valid (3 sections)\n‚úÖ requirements.md ‚Äî valid (4 requirements, all with criteria)\n‚öÝÔ∏è  design.md ‚Äî missing (acceptable for small changes)\n‚úÖ tasks.md ‚Äî valid (7 tasks)\n```"
  }
}
